drs-file
********


Description
===========

A Deployment Rule Set(DRS) is a JAR (Java ARchive) file used in Java
applications to enforce security and manage compatibility between
different versions of Java applets and web start applications (https:
//docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/technotes/guides/deploy/deployment_ru
les.html).


Available Commands
==================

* delete

* get
